# Baiduwp-PHP Project Overview

This is a PHP application that provides a web interface for accessing Baidu Netdisk files through their API. The project is built using the ThinkPHP framework.

## Key Files and Directories

- [composer.json](mdc:composer.json) - Project dependencies and configuration
- [app/](mdc:app) - Core application logic
- [config/](mdc:config) - Application configuration files
- [public/](mdc:public) - Web-accessible files
- [route/](mdc:route) - URL routing definitions
- [view/](mdc:view) - Template files
- [runtime/](mdc:runtime) - Temporary files and logs
- [extend/](mdc:extend) - Custom extensions

## Main Entry Points

- [think](mdc:think) - Command line entry point
- [public/index.php](mdc:public/index.php) - Web application entry point
- [.htaccess](mdc:.htaccess) - Apache configuration for URL rewriting

## Environment Configuration

The application uses environment variables for configuration:
- [.example.env](mdc:.example.env) - Example environment configuration

